graph LR
    MLflow[MLflow Operator]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    MLflow -->|cluster platform| K8s[Kubernetes 1.11.3+]
    MLflow -->|embedded charts| Helm[Helm v3 Engine]
    MLflow -->|runtime image| MLflowImage[MLflow v3.6.0]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional)
    MLflow -.->|TLS cert injection<br/>optional| ServiceCA[service-ca-operator]
    MLflow -.->|metadata store<br/>production| PostgreSQL[PostgreSQL 9.6+]
    MLflow -.->|artifact store<br/>production| S3[S3-compatible Storage]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    MLflow -->|traffic routing<br/>HTTPRoute| Gateway[data-science-gateway]
    MLflow -->|metrics scraping<br/>ServiceMonitor| Prometheus[Prometheus]
    MLflow -->|app menu links<br/>ConsoleLink| Console[OpenShift Console]
    MLflow -.->|user access<br/>indirect| Dashboard[ODH/RHOAI Dashboard]

    %% Integration Points
    Gateway -->|exposes| MLflowInstances[MLflow Server Instances]
    Console -->|provides links to| MLflowInstances
    Dashboard -.->|routes users via| Gateway

    %% Build Dependencies
    subgraph BuildTime["Build-time Only"]
        Go[Go 1.24.6+]
        UBI[UBI9 Base Images]
    end

    MLflow -.->|compiled with| Go
    MLflow -.->|container base| UBI

    %% Kubernetes API
    MLflow -->|core API| K8s
    MLflowInstances -->|auth checks| K8s

